{"title":"共铸民族魂","authors":["胡慧丽","胡丽伟"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":5,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"共铸民族魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡慧丽  胡丽伟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2003年的春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光依然明媚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花朵依然灿烂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2003年的春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是一个不平常的春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非典侵袭了人民的平安"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活蒙上了阴影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"街上少了坦露的笑颜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对突如其来的考验"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白衣战士挺身而出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用热血和生命保卫城市和村庄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们用生命谱写梦想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们用生命给世界留下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不朽的形象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在没有硝烟的火线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们是视死如归的英雄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们也有母子连心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们也有儿女情长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但你们说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神圣的重托在心里回响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样的使命怎么能忘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"救死扶伤是我们的职责"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么能够不去上战场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是党员，我是医生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我冲在最前方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民期待着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们智慧的灵光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在伟大祖国奔涌激荡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民期待着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们凯旋的圣火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮宇宙间的苍茫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们富饶的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在历经风霜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们美丽的家园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在飞越沧桑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的祖国，请把火炬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交到我们手上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了能够自由地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼吸和歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们手牵着手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们肩并着肩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让坚强种植坚强"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让力量传递力量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让生命挽起生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺起我们民族的脊梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是爱的同盟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们已经百炼成钢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同赴国难共铸民族的铁魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打开宇宙另一座天窗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们和衷共济"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众志成城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗击非典"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奏响华夏最强的乐章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们相信，经受风雨洗礼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五星红旗会更红更亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在世界的东方高高飘扬"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":16,"page_end":16}